\begin{figure}[!ht]
\includegraphics[width=0.6\textwidth]{../../analyses/figures/growthPreviousYearModel/bsppCurrentVSpreviousYR.jpeg}
\caption{Model slope estimates representing ring width change as a function of the current year GDD (a) and the previous year GDD (b). GDD represent the accumulated growing degree days between leafout and coloredLeaves and the models estimates shows ring width change per 7 average spring days GDD (\Sexpr{tsgddscale})
The dots represent the mean of each species and the lines, the 50\% and 90\% uncertainty intervals (UI). }
\label{fig:tsPrvsYr}
